pi.name: Sr Costa Lopes
who.comments: Global report 2020 had only provisional estimates based on Xpert data alone. The final estimates were produced in March-April 2021. The WGS analysis at WHO HQ confirmed that Mgit data could not be used. The final data in the 2021 report, is based on Xpert and WGS. However, WGS was only done for 64/917 isolates. It is unclear how these isolates where selected and hence results for INH and second-line drugs must be interpreted with caution (likely unrepresentative).
